'''''Callichroma batesi''''' is a species of [[beetle]] in the family [[Longhorn beetle|Cerambycidae]]. It was described by [[Charles Joseph Gahan|Gahan]] in 1894.<ref>Bezark, Larry G. [http://plant.cdfa.ca.gov/byciddb/bycidview.asp A Photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827211041/http://plant.cdfa.ca.gov/byciddb/bycidview.asp# |date=2013-08-27 }}. Retrieved on May 22, 2012.</ref> It is known from [[Costa Rica]] and [[Nicaragua]].<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=e6A0AQAAMAAJ&pg=PA118&dq=Callichroma+batesi&hl=en&sa=X&ei=ddb4VJ4DyY_IBJzugpgF&ved=0CB0Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Callichroma%20batesi&f=false|title=Annals and Magazine of Natural History: Including Zoology, Botany, and Geology|volume=XIV|series=6|publisher=[[Taylor & Francis]]|place=London|year=1894|page=118}}</ref>

